a restraining order.

1021
01:37:36,900 --> 01:37:39,200
When I came outside, I suddenly saw her.

1022
01:37:41,400 --> 01:37:43,400
Our eyes met.

1023
01:37:43,700 --> 01:37:45,100
She hated me.

1024
01:37:51,100 --> 01:37:54,200
Admire this beautiful symbol
of our worldly lives.

1025
01:38:08,900 --> 01:38:10,700
"And I am the death of everything

1026
01:38:11,300 --> 01:38:14,000
and I am the birth of everything.

1027
01:38:14,200 --> 01:38:17,800
Word and memory,
stability and mercifulness

1028
01:38:18,000 --> 01:38:20,200
and the silence of the secret things."

1029
01:39:28,000 --> 01:39:31,000
Sir, your father just passed away.

1030
01:39:38,500 --> 01:39:40,000
Our father is no longer alive.

1031
01:39:42,100 --> 01:39:43,200
He just passed away.

1032
01:39:47,800 --> 01:39:50,700
He left me as only president
of the group.

1033
01:39:51,300 --> 01:39:53,400
Isn't that a beautiful coincidence?

1034
01:39:54,500 --> 01:39:55,800
The president is dead!

1035
01:39:56,700 --> 01:40:00,200
Long live the president.
And tonight

1036
01:40:00,600 --> 01:40:03,400
more than  all other nights:
Love each other.

1037
01:40:11,700 --> 01:40:12,600
Oh, my sister...

1038
01:40:15,600 --> 01:40:18,000
"You cry for people
you shouldn't cry for.

1039
01:40:19,200 --> 01:40:22,600
A wise man doesn't mourn
the living or the dead,

1040
01:40:23,200 --> 01:40:24,900
since we have never been,

1041
01:40:25,100 --> 01:40:30,000
me... nor you...
nor these kings...

1042
01:40:31,100 --> 01:40:33,000
and never shall we
cease to be."

1043
01:40:46,500 --> 01:40:49,700
Finally we enter
the kingdom of princes,

1044
01:40:49,900 --> 01:40:52,700
pharaohs and gods.

1045
01:42:03,300 --> 01:42:05,100
Please, stop!

1046
01:42:39,100 --> 01:42:41,500
You had no right to treat me this way.

1047
01:42:41,900 --> 01:42:45,400
Am I more cruel than life
and creation?

1048
01:42:47,400 --> 01:42:49,800
More cruel then the Creator,
if He exists?

1049
01:42:51,300 --> 01:42:54,900
Have you watched the violence of death
on the faces of the creatures?

1050
01:42:55,800 --> 01:42:58,400
Alive we are like chained gods...

1051
01:42:59,100 --> 01:43:03,100
most of the time too cowardly
to taste real freedom.

1052
01:43:03,900 --> 01:43:05,800
Vanity of vanities.

1053
01:43:06,900 --> 01:43:08,800
Only death is the big cleansing.

1054
01:43:10,300 --> 01:43:14,200
You might have helped me
to skilfully plan

1055
01:43:14,400 --> 01:43:16,600
the fate of man.

1056
01:43:17,100 --> 01:43:19,400
You could even have brought me the sun.

1057
01:43:19,800 --> 01:43:21,300
A shame.

1058
01:43:40,900 --> 01:43:44,100
Once the divorce is settled,
you're free.

1059
01:43:45,000 --> 01:43:46,800
It will take a couple of weeks.

1060
01:44:03,400 --> 01:44:04,700
You again?

1061
01:44:05,500 --> 01:44:06,800
Leave us alone.

1062
01:44:12,100 --> 01:44:13,500
Look at me.

1063
01:44:35,600 --> 01:44:38,800
What's the use?
You don't exist anymore.

1064
01:45:04,500 --> 01:45:06,600
No, don't do that.

1065
01:45:09,100 --> 01:45:11,000
I'd see you again up there.

1066
01:45:13,300 --> 01:45:16,200
To aggravate us, me,

1067
01:45:17,400 --> 01:45:20,200
the devil and all my other fellow players.

1068
01:45:20,900 --> 01:45:24,500
To endure you until eternity...

1069
01:45:24,800 --> 01:45:26,000
How horrible.

1070
01:47:24,000 --> 01:47:29,000
The police came.
Nathalie was cuffed and taken away.

1071
01:47:30,200 --> 01:47:32,300
She never answered the question
everybody asked:

1072
01:47:32,700 --> 01:47:34,200
Why?

1073
01:47:35,800 --> 01:47:37,500
The media got on to the case,

1074
01:47:37,700 --> 01:47:40,200
but the essential truth
remained carefully hidden.

1075
01:47:41,300 --> 01:47:45,700
Nathalie was sentenced to years in jail
and the case was forgotten.

1076
01:47:47,500 --> 01:47:50,700
Married in community of property
and widowed so quickly,

1077
01:47:51,500 --> 01:47:55,900
I automatically became the heiress
of my legal husband.

1078
01:47:56,500 --> 01:48:00,500
With Charlotte I ruled the empire
here brother had wanted so badly,

1079
01:48:00,700 --> 01:48:03,900
with the expert assistance of Delacroix,

1080
01:48:04,100 --> 01:48:07,100
who proved to be a discrete
and loyal employee.

1081
01:48:07,300 --> 01:48:08,900
Life went on.

1082
01:48:10,000 --> 01:48:12,400
After her sentence, Nathalie married

1083
01:48:13,500 --> 01:48:14,800
her prison guard.

1084
01:48:15,900 --> 01:48:19,000
Of the three of us, she's the only one
who really married.

1085
01:48:21,400 --> 01:48:24,200
Years later,
I happened to see her.

1086
01:48:26,300 --> 01:48:27,700
There she was...

1087
01:48:28,300 --> 01:48:29,700
with her husband and child.

1088
01:48:33,100 --> 01:48:34,200
They all looked nice.

1089
01:48:37,700 --> 01:48:39,500
After a while we approached
each other.

1090
01:48:40,800 --> 01:48:42,300
We looked at each other.

1091
01:48:42,900 --> 01:48:43,900
In silence.

1092
01:48:47,500 --> 01:48:48,900
I only saw her.

1093
01:48:53,300 --> 01:48:55,400
Then we had to go our ways.

1094
01:48:56,500 --> 01:48:58,400
We kept looking at each other...

1095
01:48:59,500 --> 01:49:01,800
knowing it was the last time.

1096
01:49:03,600 --> 01:49:05,600
Then she bent over to me

1097
01:49:05,900 --> 01:49:07,600
and asked for forgiveness.

1098
01:49:09,300 --> 01:49:10,400
Me.

1099
01:49:12,500 --> 01:49:14,700
We looked at each other one last time

1100
01:49:15,300 --> 01:49:16,500
and then I kissed her.

1101
01:49:36,500 --> 01:49:38,800
Then she walked on,

1102
01:49:39,600 --> 01:49:41,100
with her husband and child

1103
01:49:41,800 --> 01:49:42,900
and disappeared.

1104
01:49:44,500 --> 01:49:45,400
Forever.

1105
01:50:01,400 --> 01:50:03,300
And for the rest of my life,
every day that went by,

1106
01:50:03,500 --> 01:50:05,500
I'd think about her
at least once.
